# Bitumen Hot Mix Plant Dashboard - ICA | Power BI Project

This Power BI dashboard tracks operational metrics of the Bitumen Hot Mix Plant at Indra Construction and Associates (ICA).

## 🧠 Features:
- Daily production tracking
- Bitumen temperature monitoring
- Fuel consumption trends
- Load dispatch and vehicle count
- Shift-wise operational performance

## 📁 Files:
- `HotMixPlantDashboard.pbix`: Power BI file
- `images/`: Plant overview visuals

## 🏗 Company:
**Indra Construction and Associates** – Specializing in road construction with hot mix asphalt plants, paver machines, and transport fleet.

## 🛠 Tools Used:
- Power BI
- DAX, Time Intelligence
- Excel CSV source
